======================================================
A representation X on R1 from a semantic microservices
====================================================== 
{
  "http://www.semanticweb.org/ivan/ontologies/2016/3/smsesimulator/ontology1#property10": "0101",
  "http://www.semanticweb.org/ivan/ontologies/2016/3/smsesimulator/ontology1#property11": "1010",
  "http://www.semanticweb.org/ivan/ontologies/2016/3/smsesimulator/ontology1#property12": "10101",
  "http://www.semanticweb.org/ivan/ontologies/2016/3/smsesimulator/ontology1#dscr_property1E1E2": {
    "http://www.semanticweb.org/ivan/ontologies/2016/3/smsesimulator/ontology1#property20": "10101",
    "http://www.semanticweb.org/ivan/ontologies/2016/3/smsesimulator/ontology1#property21": "0101"
  }
}

=========================================================
The representation X from R1 after API Gateway enrichment
======================================================== 
{
  "@id": "linkR1"
  "http://www.semanticweb.org/ivan/ontologies/2016/3/smsesimulator/ontology1#property10": "10101",
  "http://www.semanticweb.org/ivan/ontologies/2016/3/smsesimulator/ontology1#property11": "10101",
  "http://www.semanticweb.org/ivan/ontologies/2016/3/smsesimulator/ontology1#property12": "10101",
  "http://www.semanticweb.org/ivan/ontologies/2016/3/smsesimulator/ontology1#property1E1E2": {
    "http://www.semanticweb.org/ivan/ontologies/2016/3/smsesimulator/ontology1#property20": "1010",
    "http://www.semanticweb.org/ivan/ontologies/2016/3/smsesimulator/ontology1#property21": "0101",
    "@id": "linkR2"
  }
}

If a property is defined as an object property in the ontology, in otder to create a link to another resource, the microservice should represent that property as an object with all the necessary properties to fulfill the template.
 